author: lgo
msg: ra_serf: Fix segmentation fault when using NTLM or Negotiate authentication.
(handle_auth_header): authn headers do not always use arguments (e.g. NTLM,
Negotiate). In these cases, just use the header value as is.

author: dws
msg: * STATUS: Nominate r36834 for inclusion in 1.6.1.

author: dws
msg: Changes to build Subversion 1.7 and 1.6.x for RHEL4.
* packages/rpm/rhel-4/apache.patch : Subversion is not correctly doing the
APACHE <-> APR version checking.  This fixes the apache_minor_version
regex and changes AP_SERVER_MINORVERSION_NUMBER to AP_SERVER_MINORVERSION.
* packages/rpm/rhel-4/python-2.4.patch : Change find_python.sh to find the
non-RHEL4 python-2.4 before the normal installed 2.3 version.
* packages/rpm/rhel-4/subversion.spec : Normal changes to SPEC file to
accomodate new required versions of packages and fixes to build on trunk
